profile:
Whether you are cleaning your office, maintaining a large institution, beginning new construction, recovering from a natural disaster or cleaning up a moldy basement, Sublime Mold Prevention and Remediation can help. Our products can clean and protect a variety of building materials of microbial residues and contamination.


We offer an industry-leading warranty of 30 years on existing structures and 50 years on new builds.
